{"tid":1838060,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有人戴黑色海棉口罩","createTime":"2020-01-24T01:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T08:24:11.000Z","uid":165028,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1692392af6167cee3be1546db9bd0c20b25d2ca3","tid":1838060,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:23:04.000Z","msg":"都講左好多次防唔到菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戴就戴款正常外科口罩啦"},{"pid":"c598d61314bbd8d85c3a35b65adebd54a760ec8f","tid":1838060,"uid":198590,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:23:09.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#165028 - 離地中產</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>周街都貼連豬搞到心都煩哂 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>睇見隻豬就火滾想撕左佢</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1677596/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1677596/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>誠哥真係好醒目 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>開金口講句要對年青人網開一面<br />\n而家旗下百佳, 豐澤等避開一劫<br />\n如果唔係被暴徒燒毀打爛唔知幾多間<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fsosad.gif&h=5e5c7195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我而家見到黑衫蒙面阻住我架車都唔出聲屌佢地<br />\n作狀支持佢地俾個like 等佢地放行<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fclown.gif&h=b82ebc3d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1628499/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1628499/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>想同琴晚太子站嘅一個勇武道歉 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>因為我當時太驚又怕死<br />\n所以同其他乘客撞你出門口<br />\n希望你無事<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Ffrown.gif&h=dc0d24e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原諒我<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1526091/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1526091/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>好怕d勇武派 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>街上面見到佢地都會避之則吉<br />\n怕會招惹埋d警察<br />\n琴日黃大仙站成班又面罩又防具咁衝入車廂<br />\n嚇到我下個站即刻落車</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1503651/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1503651/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>（求屌醒）一直唔明白你地搞抗爭做咩 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>我80後 本身都係中產階級 收入穩定又係專業人士<br />\n雖然近呢個月都聽左好多理據話要爭取好多野<br />\n包括撤回逃犯條例 調整警權過大 之類<br />\n但係我就唔明點解一定要搞到武力衝突先收手<br />\n再加上止舉令警民官民矛盾越來越大 對香港真係好咩<br />\n<br />\n點解要搞咁多野 真心唔明每個星期搞一兩單衝突暴動真係好咩 已經港九新界都搞砸哂<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fsosad.gif&h=5e5c7195&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1320673/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1320673/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/4Re5r6q.png\" />"},{"pid":"bbc3157e179895f3f1a2d8dc31f877339e630ee8","tid":1838060,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:24:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，市民會支持你地既決定</span></span><br />\n<br />\n支唔支持醫護大罷工？<br />\nA: 支持，連OT 都無，冒咁大風險,會死人！<br />\nB: 唔支持，置市民安危於不顧，不道德<br />\n<br />\n仲等咩, 快黎投票啦!<br />\n分享自香港地投票 HKVOTE<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/Topic.php?id=1008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org%2FTopic.php%3Fid%3D1008&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX9Rt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=317db85c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org/Topic.php?id=1008</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫手Wtsapp, FB 散出去</span></span><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n入黎幫手推十次<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"a0938a4b9c2ef02286642e231e89aa5f1a94b6c7","tid":1838060,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:25:09.000Z","msg":"係咪姐係kf 94"},{"pid":"7a40821b4c88811403f1d2b5ceeb4972dbfb61a4","tid":1838060,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:26:52.000Z","msg":"推 , 人命尼"},{"pid":"7a064724a9c86fa5850ed15bc28f6d339216223e","tid":1838060,"uid":5443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0938a4b9c2ef02286642e231e89aa5f1a94b6c7","tid":1838060,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:25:09.000Z","msg":"係咪姐係kf 94"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:30:14.000Z","msg":"唔係，遊行好多人戴嗰隻"},{"pid":"aaa37dca8a3c652ec42be50df37d666735384c56","tid":1838060,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:30:34.000Z","msg":"推返上熱門！<br />\n<br />\n「突發」四個醫療工會不排除於初四後發起工業行動！(終極整合）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837445</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c343